  "title": "A round orange UFO hovered over Curitiba [2000]*",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/15/a-round-orange-ufo-hovered-over-curitiba-2000/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-tZ",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JAN 13th, 2000</strong>. Time: 23h50pm. Duration: 01 hour. In the Xaxim neighborhood, in Curitiba, State of Paraná, under a partially cloudy sky, several witnesses observed an unidentified round flying object with an orange color. According to the witnesses&#8217; reports, the UFO remained stationary for as long as it was observed. The COMDABRA&#8217;s [Brazilian Aerospace Defense Command] report tells that: &#8220;He informed that many nieghbors in his street were also watching.&#8221;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.570. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Avistamento de ovni no bairro de Xaxim, cidade de Curitiba, Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>JAN 13th, 2000. Time: 23h50pm. Duration: 01 hour. In the Xaxim neighborhood, in Curitiba, State of Paraná, under a partially cloudy sky, several witnesses observed an unidentified round flying object with an orange color. According to the witnesses&#8217; reports, the UFO remained stationary for as long as it was observed. The COMDABRA&#8217;s [Brazilian Aerospace Defense [&hellip;]</p>\n",
